On this journey, Pwnky's Comic ear ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Blonde hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Hat with leafs  hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Glasses, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
